  "instructions": [
    "Rinse quinoa under cold water and drain well.",
    "In a large skillet or wok, heat vegan butter or olive oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add onions and bell peppers; sauté until translucent about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in crushed tomatoes, dates, lemon juice, cumin, and oregano. Mix well.",
    "Gradually add quinoa to the skillet while stirring constantly for about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste. Serve hot, garnished with pine nuts if desired.",
    "Enjoy your homemade Iflaky Zesty Dates Pilaf!"
